<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10098395>
    dc:description "FIGURES 155–165. Thrips species. T. nonakai sp. n., female. 155–161: (155) Head & pronotum; (156) Antenna, right; (157) Mesonotum & metascutum; (158) Fore wing, right; (159) Tergite VI & pleurotergite, right side; (160) Tergites VIII–X; (161) Sternite VI. T. nonakai sp. n., male 162–163: (162) Tergites VIII–IX; (163) Sternites III–V, sculpture omitted. T. ogasawarensis sp. n., female 164–165: (164) Head & pronotum; (165) Antenna, right." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10098395/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10098397>
    dc:description "FIGURES 166–178. Thrips species. T. ogasawarensis sp. n., female 166–168: (166) Metascutum; (167) Tergite VIII; (168) Sternite VII, sculpture omitted. T. ogasawarensis sp. n., male 169––170: (169) Tergites VIII–IX, sculpture omitted; (170) Sternite VII, sculpture omitted. T. orientalis, female 171–176: (171) Head & pronotum; (172) Antenna, right; (173) Metascutum; (174) Tergite IV & pleurotergite, left side; (175) Tergite VIII; (176) Sternites V–VII, sculpture omitted. T. orientalis, male 177–178: (177) Tergite IX and left side of segment X; (178) Sternite VI, sculpture omitted." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10098397/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

